SUMMARY:Yell Out Fest – Friday Show 25$
LOCATION:4848 St-Laurent (métro Laurier)
DESCRIPTION:2026-03-06 19:00:00\n\n4848 St-Laurent (métro Laurier)\n\nhtt
 ps://www.openstreetmap.org/way/352197557\n\nCINNAMON (Albany)\nANÉANTIX (
 Québec)\nHEAT RASH (Hamilton)\nNUCLEAR FAMILY\nKOFFIN BYRTH (Ottawa)\nTHE
  PITS\nCESNA\n&nbsp\;\n$25 one show\, $40 friday + saturday\n&nbsp\;\nYell
  Out is a D.I.Y. festival. Together we stand for feminism\, solidarity and
  respect within and beyond the punk community. We want to embrace the voic
 es and presence of women\, trans women\, non-binary\, genderqueer\, and al
 l folks who are not hetero cis males.\nAll profit from the fest will be sp
 lit between two organizations: Ele Elna Elak (a volunteer-driven initiativ
 e dedicated to supporting Palestinian families in need) and Chez Doris (a 
 Montreal-based organization that offers a safe\, non-discriminatory space 
 where women can receive support to regain their dignity and rebuild their 
 lives).\n&nbsp\;\nPart of Yell Out Fest 2026\nSaturday Punk Market + Works
 hops (Les Révoltes)\nFeminist Comedy Show (Casa del Popolo)\nSaturday Sho
 w (La Sotterenea)
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.openstreetmap.org/way/352197557
END:VEVENT
